22. Hercules: here follows a comparison between the victories oi Hercules and those oi Epicurus. Eight oi the labors oi Hercules are referred to, the slaying ol the Nemaean lion, the capture oi the Erymanthian boar, the bringing oi the Cretan bull to Erystheus, the destruction oi the Lernean hydra, the ietching oi the oxen oi Geryon, the driving away oi the Stymphalian birds, the taking oi the fiesh- eating mares of the Thracian Diomede to Mycenae, the finding and carrying off of the golden apples oi the Hesperides.
